，中方回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5246957d1f7b14f68f82193d54f26390_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "210 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/631450184"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8+aGprr5hpRREAMaCTEwMjYwMTAxNSCezfqqBjAAOIgBQAVyCTYzMTQ1MDE4NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1700722984.420970", "card_id": "Q_631007149", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "坚持运动让人看起来不显老的原理是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3ec0f332202aec5b29fb66a03372f329_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/631007149"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8+aGprr5hpRREAMaCTEwMjUwMjY2OSCdnO2qBjAAOEtABnIJNjMxMDA3MTQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1700722984.422578", "card_id": "Q_284979676", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些已经被毁掉的文物珍宝？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ffbf3b7c39127c59a3bd413aeb35f14b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "